Creator Vikas Bahl

Directed by Abhishek Sengupta

Written by Vikas Bahl. Nikhil Arora. Aarti Kapoor. Tahira Nath. Kalyani Pandit. Chaitally Parmar

Cast Samridhi Dewan( Maya Ahuja9 episodes, 2022 ). Vaibhav Raj Gupta( Sahil Mistry9 episodes, 2022 ). Gul Panag( Zaina Mistry9 episodes, 2022 ). Namrata Sheth( Jhilmil Lohia9 episodes, 2022 ). Himanshi Pandey( Mikita9 episodes, 2022 ). Kenisha Awasthi( Meeshu Chawla4 episodes, 2022 ). Amy Aela( Aanchal3 episodes, 2022 ). Baljinder Kaur( Chugh Aunti2 episodes, 2022 ). Monica Chaudhary( Heena1 episode, 2022 ). Jitendra Singh Rajpurohit( Inspector (Airport)1 episode, 2022 ). Sheeba Chaddha(unknown episodes ). Zain Khan Durrani( Prithvi Banerjeeunknown episodes ). Soham Majumdar( Dr. Punitunknown episodes ). Aradhya Ajana(unknown episodes ). Rajendra Sethi(unknown episodes)

Language Hindi

Producers Vikas Bahl. Abhay S. Dutta. Aditya Jayesh Gandhi. Varun Khandelwal. Wrickved Mukherjee. Sumit S. Rajput. Anurag Shrivastava

Official site sonyLIV

Season 1

Total Episodes 9
